slike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"今日劇本猜測:  <br />\n<br />\n下午/入夜開始有在場人仕 叫出「死曱甴」「暴徒」「唔讀書」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例句: 1. 唔知班「死曱甴」「暴徒」有冇出黎投票<br />\n          2. 「死曱甴」 投黎到冇用<br />\n<br />\n目的: 挑引在場人仕，由其而家將年青身份證分另一條隊排。  警方會將「擾亂」分子拘捕，姐係將成條Y/Z身份證 既人拉哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下一步: 另一方陣營係大拘捕之後用旅遊巴將一車車既選民推去投票站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家記住，你今日角色係一個廢老廢青，只投建制派，所有野都聽唔到，睇唔到。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「我真係外賣仔黎架」</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果仲未明，請睇完一次「演員的自我修養」先好出去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5f4af70caa5f1df2307f0859b81c2cb126ff31","tid":1749462,"uid":65854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MbUs4Qm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbUs4Qm.jpg&h=41958794&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a88c195315221530943080e57835df5b4e2cead","tid":1749462,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"抵你一世係TVB仲二打六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做戲又廢又垃圾"},{"pid":"1cd4bbf9d873a2589866bec7ea22b67db71f9867","tid":1749462,"uid":180397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"又係呢條垃圾"},{"pid":"e2a8b1e10eee2a749be975fd5d73b01b938bd1d8","tid":1749462,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"一睇就知有利益乜人都可以出賣的人"},{"pid":"297f9ef9b369a2f1a0fd57d74ce08f3fb72e3b20","tid":1749462,"uid":257366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"